BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE:Knobstone Hiking Trail Association
UID:event_314659811@meetup.com
SEQUENCE:1
DTSTAMP:20260513T033029Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260530T090000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260530T150000
SUMMARY:Knobstone Adopters Work Day
DESCRIPTION:Knobstone Hiking Trail Association of Indiana Meetup\n**KHTA V
 olunteers & Adopters Workdays – May 30 & June 27**\n\n[![](https://www.k
 nobstonehikingtrail.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/20260228_1148531-1-196x
 300.jpg)](https://www.knobstonehikingtrail.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/
 20260228_1148531-1.jpg)We have made considerable progress since the beginn
 ing of the year clearing trail\, building drains\, and chainsawing blowdow
 ns from mile 32 to 34+. We will continue maintenance of the trail on the N
 orth side of Highway 56\nDetails will be posted here\, on Meetup\, and Fac
 ebook. We will continue to meet on the North side of Hwy 56 at the trail c
 rossing.\nFor Google directions\, click on [Highway 56 Trail Crossing](htt
 ps://maps.app.goo.gl/Pm8WyrtSzUbcerDk9)\nPlease bring a lunch and water. W
 e will have large hand tools\, you may bring any small tools you have such
  as clippers or a pruning saw. And a backpack is handy to carry everything
  in. Instructions will be provided for those who need them. We will finish
  at about 3:00 pm.\n\nJoin us on our website at [http://www.knobstonehikin
 gtrail.org/](http://www.knobstonehikingtrail.org/) and on Facebook at [KHT
 A Facebook Group.](https://www.facebook.com/groups/2255586117953484/)
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/knobstone-hiking-trail-association-of
 -indiana-meetup/events/314659811/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20260506T151712Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260506T151712Z
CLASS:PUBLIC
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE:Knobstone Hiking Trail Association
UID:event_314127595@meetup.com
SEQUENCE:1
DTSTAMP:20260513T033029Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260607T100000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260607T130000
SUMMARY:Hike of the Tecumseh Trail extension as a
DESCRIPTION:Knobstone Hiking Trail Association of Indiana Meetup\nCome hik
 e the just built section of the Tecumseh Trail extension. The Trail is lin
 ear but we can use forest roads to make it a loop. The gate at Hatfield Ri
 dge Road should be open so we’ll meet at the parking lot at the end of t
 he road. If people want\, we can go to lunch at Indy’s nearby when we ge
 t done. This is a beautiful section of trail so be sure to come.
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/knobstone-hiking-trail-association-of
 -indiana-meetup/events/314127595/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20260405T010642Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260405T010642Z
CLASS:PUBLIC
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE:Knobstone Hiking Trail Association
UID:event_312918122@meetup.com
SEQUENCE:1
DTSTAMP:20260513T033029Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260613T091500
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260613T151500
SUMMARY:2nd Weekend Work Day Trail Building
DESCRIPTION:Knobstone Hiking Trail Association of Indiana Meetup\nWould yo
 u to spend a day in some beautiful woods with a delightful group of people
  building a connecting section of Indiana’s premier long distance hiking
  trail? Come join us as we continue work on the Tecumseh Trail extension p
 ortion of the KHT in MMSF. We will be building the new trail including cli
 pping green briar.\nPlease bring a lunch and water. We will have large han
 d tools\, but please bring any small tools you have such as clippers or a 
 pruning saw. And a backpack is handy to carry everything in. Instructions 
 will be provided for those who need them. We finish about 3:30.\nMeet at t
 he Hatfield Ridge Road gate. The gate is locked but we have a key. Go to t
 he big sign on Rosenbaum/Catholic Cemetry Rd.\nJoin us on our website at h
 ttp://www.knobstonehikingtrail.org/\, on Facebook at [www.facebook.com/gro
 ups/2255586117953484](http://www.facebook.com/groups/2255586117953484)\, a
 nd Substack [https://khta.substack.com/](https://khta.substack.com/)
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/knobstone-hiking-trail-association-of
 -indiana-meetup/events/312918122/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20260116T195308Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260116T195308Z
CLASS:PUBLIC
END:VEVENT
